seng202.group6.importer

Class FlightImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.group6.importer.DataImporter<FlightPoint>
      • seng202.group6.importer.FlightImporter

  • public class FlightImporter
extends DataImporter<FlightPoint>
    This class is for importing flight csv files and converting them into a Flight. This class will also create a list of lines (with errors) that are in the incorrect format.
